Game Package.

Where the magic happens, really.

Here the game's model, view and controller unite their codes to bring the game to life.

MODEL:
	Holds game values:
		- Seed;
		- Maps;
		- Agents (Hero, Creatures, Itens, etc).

VIEW:
	Use Draw and Assets to draw suff on the screen:
		- UI;
		- Menus;
		- Background (walls, floors, shadows, etc);
		- Foreground (Itens, Creatures, Hero, etc).

CONTROLLER:
	Modify Model's values:
		- Control Agents (Hero, Creatures, stuff);
		- Activate effects (Hard to explain, but poison or bleed is a good example);
		- Generate Maps (?);
		- Do stuff.